; Coverage for commodity.cc lines 436-442: price comparison with same price commodity
; Two lots with the same price commodity ($) but different values ($100 vs $200)
; Exercises the less-than and greater-than price comparison paths

2024/01/01 Buy
    Assets:Brokerage    10 AAPL {$100.00}
    Assets:Checking

2024/01/15 Buy More
    Assets:Brokerage    5 AAPL {$200.00}
    Assets:Checking

test bal --lots Assets:Brokerage
      10 AAPL {$100}
       5 AAPL {$200}  Assets:Brokerage
end test
